236
00:12:54,609 --> 00:12:55,609
Itu benar!

237
00:12:55,609 --> 00:12:57,909
Tapi kami hanya menggunakan bagian luar rumah itu.

238
00:12:57,909 --> 00:12:59,709
Kami menggunakan set ketika kami syuting di dalam.

239
00:12:59,709 --> 00:13:00,809
Begitu?

240
00:13:00,809 --> 00:13:02,109
Aku mengerti!

241
00:13:03,009 --> 00:13:05,909
